Game.....: Caesar's Palace 2000
Origin...: USA - NTSC
Released.: September 21st, 2000
Ripped.......: Nothing

The only gambling simulation worthy of the Caesars Palace name. A heart-pounding 3D universe of fun awaits including dealers with personality that actually make you feel like you're in the world famous Las Vegas Casino. So realistic you might think it's a role playing game! Here's where you become a High-Roller and get to "Go Behind The Velvet Ropes" to experience the roller-coaster ride called high stakes gambling. 